data.description: Luxurious updated home on extra-large lot with auto driveway gate and 3-car garage. Gorgeous kitchen with sleek quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances including double ovens, 36” 5-burner gas cooktop, wine chiller, and ample storage space. Spacious living with tray ceilings and gas log fireplace with stunning views of the backyard oasis, including a resort-style heated swimming pool, hot tub and a spacious patio area for lounging. Don’t miss the pool/party house or guest quarters behind the garage with a living area, large dry bar with min fridge, wine chiller, full bath with shower and split A/C and heat. The luxurious primary suite features an en-suite bath with soaking tub, walk-in shower with rain shower heads and an expansive walk-in closet with custom storage. The downstairs study offers a quiet environment with double French doors. Upstairs is a large game room and a flex room, maybe for a home gym, hobby room, or a playroom for the kids, plus 4 more bedrooms.
